contents.item: The more you overthink the less you will understand.
You know, it is a little known fact that thinking is entirely overrated. The world would be a much better place if we all did a lot less of it.
contents.owner: Laurie Viera Rigler, Confessions of a Jane Austen Addict

contents.item: I can’t help but think,’ Park would say during taekwando. ‘I can’t turn off my brain.
